{
    "title": "AegisAI - LLM Observability Dashboard",
    "description": "Comprehensive monitoring dashboard for AegisAI - The Black Box Flight Recorder for LLM Applications",
    "widgets": [
        {
            "definition": {
                "type": "note",
                "content": "## üõ°Ô∏è LLM Health Overview\\n\\n**What Healthy LLM Operations Look Like:**\\n\\n‚úÖ **Latency**: \u003c 2000ms (P95)\\n‚úÖ **Risk Level**: Majority at 0 (low risk)\\n‚úÖ **Error Rate**: \u003c 1% of requests\\n‚úÖ **Token Usage**: Steady, predictable patterns\\n\\n**Key Signals to Watch:**\\n- **Prompt Risk**: Spikes indicate potential security threats\\n- **Latency Trends**: Sudden increases may signal API issues\\n- **Token Spikes**: Could indicate abuse or unusually long prompts\\n- **Error Count**: Zero is ideal; investigate any errors immediately\\n\\n**This dashboard tracks real-time LLM security and performance metrics via StatsD.**",
                "background_color": "blue",
                "font_size": "14",
                "text_align": "left",
                "show_tick": false,
                "tick_pos": "50%",
                "tick_edge": "left"
            }
        },
        {
            "definition": {
                "type": "timeseries",
                "requests": [
                    {
                        "q": "sum:aegisai.request.latency{*}",
                        "display_type": "line",
                        "style": {
                            "palette": "dog_classic",
                            "line_type": "solid",
                            "line_width": "normal"
                        }
                    }
                ],
                "title": "Request Latency Over Time (StatsD)",
                "show_legend": true,
                "legend_size": "0"
            }
        },
        {
            "definition": {
                "type": "query_value",
                "requests": [
                    {
                        "q": "avg:aegisai.request.latency{*}",
                        "aggregator": "avg"
                    }
                ],
                "title": "Average Response Latency",
                "precision": 0
            }
        },
        {
            "definition": {
                "type": "timeseries",
                "requests": [
                    {
                        "q": "sum:aegisai.tokens.count{*}.as_count()",
                        "display_type": "bars",
                        "style": {
                            "palette": "purple",
                            "line_type": "solid",
                            "line_width": "normal"
                        }
                    }
                ],
                "title": "Token Usage Over Time"
            }
        },
        {
            "definition": {
                "type": "timeseries",
                "requests": [
                    {
                        "q": "sum:aegisai.tokens.used{*}",
                        "display_type": "bars",
                        "style": {
                            "palette": "purple",
                            "line_type": "solid",
                            "line_width": "normal"
                        }
                    }
                ],
                "title": "Token Usage Over Time (StatsD)"
            }
        },
        {
            "definition": {
                "type": "query_value",
                "requests": [
                    {
                        "q": "sum:aegisai.request.count{*}",
                        "aggregator": "sum"
                    }
                ],
                "title": "Total Requests",
                "precision": 0
            }
        },
        {
            "definition": {
                "type": "timeseries",
                "requests": [
                    {
                        "q": "sum:aegisai.request.error{*}.as_count()",
                        "display_type": "bars",
                        "style": {
                            "palette": "warm"
                        }
                    }
                ],
                "title": "Error Count Over Time"
            }
        },
        {
            "definition": {
                "type": "timeseries",
                "requests": [
                    {
                        "q": "avg:aegisai.prompt.risk{*} by {severity}",
                        "display_type": "line",
                        "style": {
                            "palette": "semantic"
                        }
                    }
                ],
                "title": "Prompt Risk Level (0=Low, 1=Medium, 2=High)"
            }
        },
        {
            "definition": {
                "type": "toplist",
                "requests": [
                    {
                        "q": "top(sum:aegisai.tokens.used{*} by {malicious}.as_count(), 10, 'mean', 'desc')"
                    }
                ],
                "title": "Token Usage by Request Type"
            }
        },
        {
            "definition": {
                "type": "event_timeline",
                "query": "source:aegisai priority:all",
                "title": "Incident Timeline"
            }
        },
        {
            "definition": {
                "type": "log_stream",
                "query": "service:aegisai status:warn",
                "columns": [
                    "host",
                    "service",
                    "@prompt_injection",
                    "@matched_patterns"
                ],
                "title": "Malicious Prompts Log Stream",
                "show_date_column": true,
                "show_message_column": true,
                "message_display": "expanded-md"
            }
        },
        {
            "definition": {
                "type": "query_value",
                "requests": [
                    {
                        "q": "sum:aegisai.tokens.count{*}",
                        "aggregator": "sum"
                    }
                ],
                "title": "Total Tokens Consumed",
                "precision": 0
            }
        },
        {
            "definition": {
                "type": "timeseries",
                "requests": [
                    {
                        "q": "sum:aegisai.tokens.count{malicious:true}.as_count()",
                        "display_type": "bars",
                        "style": {
                            "palette": "warm"
                        }
                    },
                    {
                        "q": "sum:aegisai.tokens.count{malicious:false}.as_count()",
                        "display_type": "bars",
                        "style": {
                            "palette": "cool"
                        }
                    }
                ],
                "title": "Safe vs Malicious Requests"
            }
        },
        {
            "definition": {
                "type": "check_status",
                "title": "AegisAI Health Status",
                "check": "aegisai.backend.health",
                "grouping": "cluster",
                "tags": [
                    "*"
                ]
            }
        }
    ],
    "template_variables": [
        {
            "name": "env",
            "default": "dev",
            "prefix": "env"
        }
    ],
    "layout_type": "ordered",
    "is_read_only": false,
    "notify_list": [],
    "tags": [
        "service:aegisai",
        "team:platform"
    ]
}